  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC440">
        <l>avaitām</l>
	<l>tattaṅ kuṟippi ṉeccañ ceppum.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/244/mode/1up">244</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/244/mode/1up">244</ref>.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, itu 'kuṟippē icaiyē' (tol. col. eccavi - 34) yeṉṟu kūṟappaṭṭa iraṇṭeccamum taṅkuṟippiṟpaṟṟiya eccattāṉē muṭipu kūṟappaṭum, piṟitillai eṉpatu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu : 'viṇṇeṉa vicaittatu' kuṟippeccam ; atu taṉ kuṟippiṉaiyē koṇṭu muṭintatu.</p>
<p>viṇṇeṉṟatē vicaittatu eṉappaṭṭatu. ataṉāl tattaṅkuṟippiṉ eccattāṉē muṭintatu eṉpatu.</p>
<p>iṉi, icaiyeccam, olleṉa volittatu. iṭaiccollōttuḷ aṟupakutiya eṉṟu ōtappaṭṭa eṉa vikaṟpittu iraṇṭu muṭipu kūṟappaṭṭa teṉpatu. maṟṟu āṇṭuc colleccam eṉpatillaiyāl eṉiṉ, viṭai,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC440-Iḷam-cit1">
<l>'eṉave ṉeccam viṉaiyoṭu muṭimē'</l></lg>	<p>(tol. col. eccavi - 42)</p>
<p>eṉṟu muṭittār. viṉaiyeṉa viṉai piṉṉun taṉkaṇṇatē colleccam, atukoṇṭu muṭital ivvāypāṭu, av vēṟṟumai nōkki vēṟu colleccam eṉa vēṇṭiṉār eṉpatu.</p>
<p>muṉṉar mūṉṟumēl vantu muṭikkum eñcu poruṭkiḷaviyila eṉa, oṉṟu uṭaittu eṉpatu paṭṭuniṉṟatu ; aḵtiyātō colleccam eṉpatu.</p>
<p>iṉi, ataṟku muṭipu kūṟukiṉṟār.	(44)</p>
 </body>
  </text>

